description:
The Met-Care Services include:

24 Hour Emergency Medical Assistance
• MET-ALERT App;
• Emergency telephone medical assistance to guide you through Cardiopulmonary Resuscitation / First Aid;
• Light and heavy motor vehicle rescues, including extrication;
• Emergency Medical care at the scene, stabilization and definitive treatment;
• Emergency medical transportation to the nearest appropriate hospital with coverage both inside and outside the company premises during the company's activities;
• Coverage inside and outside the school premises, during the activities of the day care, school or university;
•	Coverage within the city of Luanda.

Additional benefits:
• Medical support at company events;
• Level I First Aid Training for 1 company member per year;
• Annual emergency exercises at the company's premises;
• Annual demonstration of CPR and ambulance;
• MET-CARE representatives to discuss health and safety issues in preschool;
• An annual welcome pack including posters and stickers for vehicles.
